== 功能 ==
滑液關節的動作可以有：
* 外展：遠離身體中線的動作。
* 內收：移近身體中線的動作。
* 伸展：在關節處伸直肢體。
* 屈曲：在關節處彎曲肢體。
* 旋轉：圍繞定點的圓周運動。

== 臨床意義 ==
關節間隙等於關節內骨骼之間的距離。關節間隙變窄是[[骨關節炎|骨關節炎]]和發炎性退化的徵兆<ref name="JacobsonGirish2008">{{cite journal|last1=Jacobson|first1=Jon A.|last2=Girish|first2=Gandikota|last3=Jiang|first3=Yebin|last4=Sabb|first4=Brian J.|title=Radiographic Evaluation of Arthritis: Degenerative Joint Disease and Variations|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_radiology_2008-09_248_3/page/737|journal=Radiology|volume=248|issue=3|year=2008|pages=737–747|issn=0033-8419|doi=10.1148/radiol.2483062112}}</ref>。正常的關節間隙在髖關節（上[[髖臼|髖臼]]處）至少2mm<ref name="Lequesne2004">{{cite journal|last1=Lequesne|first1=M|title=The normal hip joint space: variations in width, shape, and architecture on 223 pelvic radiographs|journal=Annals of the Rheumatic Diseases|volume=63|issue=9|year=2004|pages=1145–1151|issn=0003-4967|doi=10.1136/ard.2003.018424|pmc=1755132}}</ref>，在膝關節至少3mm<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=YfFj8Gbq5H0C&pg=PA6 Page 6] in: {{cite book|title=Osteoarthritis: Diagnosis and Medical/surgical Management, LWW Doody's all reviewed collection|url=https://archive.org/details/osteoarthritisdi0000unse|author=Roland W. Moskowitz|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|year=2007|isbn=9780781767071}}</ref>，在肩關節至少4到5mm<ref>{{cite web|url=http://radref.org/ref.php?id=361|title=Glenohumeral joint space|website=radref.org|access-date=2019-11-29|archive-date=2020-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207051958/http://radref.org/ref.php?id=361|dead-url=no}}, in turn citing: {{cite journal|last1=Petersson|first1=Claes J.|last2=Redlund-Johnell|first2=Inga|title=Joint Space in Normal Gleno-Humeral Radiographs|journal=Acta Orthopaedica Scandinavica|volume=54|issue=2|year=2009|pages=274–276|issn=0001-6470|doi=10.3109/17453678308996569}}</ref>，顳頜關節在1.5到4mm之間<ref name="Massilla ManiSivasubramanian2016">{{cite journal|last1=Massilla Mani|first1=F.|last2=Sivasubramanian|first2=S. Satha|title=A study of temporomandibular joint osteoarthritis using computed tomographic imaging|journal=Biomedical Journal|volume=39|issue=3|year=2016|pages=201–206|issn=2319-4170|doi=10.1016/j.bj.2016.06.003|pmc=6138784}}</ref>。因此，關節間隙變窄的程度是骨關節炎的放射學分類要素之一。

